baby":false,"eggs":["water2"],"flavor":[{"version":"ruby","text":"CARVANHA\u2019s strongly developed jaws and its sharply pointed fangs pack the destructive power to rip out boat hulls. Many boats have been attacked and sunk by this POK\u00e9MON."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"If anything invades CARVANHA\u2019s territory, it will swarm and tear at the intruder with its pointed fangs. On its own, however, this POK\u00e9MON turns suddenly timid."},{"version":"emerald","text":"CARVANHA attack ships in swarms, making them sink. Although it is said to be a very vicious POK\u00e9MON, it timidly flees as soon as it finds itself alone."},{"version":"firered","text":"It lives in massive rivers that course through jungles. It swarms prey that enter its territory."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It lives in massive rivers that course through jungles. It swarms prey that enter its territory."},{"version":"diamond","text":"They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."},{"version":"pearl","text":"They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."},{"version":"platinum","text":"They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"They form packs to attack boats and rip out their hulls to sink them. They live in rivers in the jungle."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"They form packs to attack boats and rip out their hulls to sink them. They live in rivers in the jungle."},{"version":"black","text":"They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."},{"version":"white","text":"They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."},{"version":"black-2","text":"They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."},{"version":"white-2","text":"They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."},{"version":"x","text":"They form packs to attack boats and rip out their hulls to sink them. They live in rivers in the jungle."},{"version":"y","text":"It lives in massive rivers that course through jungles. It swarms prey that enter its territory."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Carvanha\u2019s strongly developed jaws and its sharply pointed fangs pack the destructive power to rip out boat hulls. Many boats have been attacked and sunk by this Pok\u00e9mon."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"If anything invades Carvanha\u2019s territory, it will swarm and tear at the intruder with its pointed fangs. On its own, however, this Pok\u00e9mon turns suddenly timid."},{"version":"sun","text":"Each school has its own territory. Any intruders are mercilessly attacked with fangs bared."},{"version":"moon","text":"If they scent the faintest trace of blood, they rush to attack en masse. When alone, they\u2019re rather cowardly."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"They\u2019re such cowards that they won\u2019t hunt alone. When five or so of them get together, they suddenly turn ferocious!"},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"With its sturdy jaws and fangs, it can easily chomp wooden boats to splinters. It fights with Basculin over food."},{"version":"sword","text":"It won\u2019t attack while it\u2019s alone\u2014not even if it spots prey. Instead, it waits for other Carvanha to join it, and then the Pok\u00e9mon attack as a group."},{"version":"shield","text":"These Pok\u00e9mon have sharp fangs and powerful jaws. Sailors avoid Carvanha dens at all costs."}],"evo":{"name":"carvanha","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"sharpedo","level":1,"min_level":30,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"kn